#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:93 3026fdad7dd2496e94d7865234d77daa
msgid "Important: IRQ when using interrupt receive"
msgstr "重要说明：使用中断接收时的 IRQ 行为"

#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:97 52649244be494dbaa16cd05485ca542c
msgid ""
"When receiving data with the interrupt method (``set_irq_callback`` and "
"``start_recv()``), the firmware automatically clears the LoRa IRQ flag "
"after interrupt handling."
msgstr ""
"当使用中断方式（``set_irq_callback`` 与 ``start_recv()``）接收数据时，"
"程序会在处理完成后 **自动清除 LoRa IRQ**。"

#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:101 6a47cbd67b354a87992566360d3252c8
msgid ""
"In this case, polling ``irq_triggered()`` may always return ``False`` "
"because the flag has already been cleared. This is not a receive failure."
msgstr ""
"在这种情况下，轮询 ``irq_triggered()`` 经常会 **一直返回** ``False``："
"这是因为标志位已经被清除，并不代表接收失败。"

#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:104 5aa1b066b17d4b6499e05cae98638d1b
msgid "Please use synchronous receive mode (``recv()``) for testing."
msgstr "请使用同步接收模式（``recv()``）进行测试。"

