"Bandwidth, options include:  - ``\"7.8\"``: 7.8 KHz - ``\"10.4\"``: 10.4 "
"KHz - ``\"15.6\"``: 15.6 KHz - ``\"20.8\"``: 20.8 KHz - ``\"31.25\"``: "
"31.25 KHz - ``\"41.7\"``: 41.7 KHz - ``\"62.5\"``: 62.5 KHz - "
"``\"125\"``: 125 KHz - ``\"250\"``: 250 KHz - ``\"500\"``: 500 KHz"
