#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:380 5756e42f2fee4ba4aca547e51bde801f
msgid "Check IRQ trigger."
msgstr "检查 IRQ 触发。"

#: ../../source/hardware/lora.rst:382 8b805fd5578844ca8efc7d4485733285
msgid ""
"Returns ``True`` if an interrupt service routine (ISR) has been triggered"
" since the last send or receive started. In **interrupt receive** mode "
"the IRQ is usually cleared inside the driver when the callback runs, so "
"this method may stay ``False``. Use synchronous ``recv()`` to test "
"reception (see the note above)."
msgstr ""
"如果自上次开始发送或接收以来触发过中断服务程序（ISR），则返回 ``True``。在**中断接收**模式下，回调执行时驱动通常会清除 "
"IRQ，因此该方法可能一直为 ``False``。测试接收请使用同步 ``recv()`` （见上方说明）。"

